tourBios.otherCarHigh: 2011 Pac-West Player of the Year, Freshman of the Year and conference medalist while at the University of Hawaii-Hilo...Was the 2013 Itani Invitational champion...Earned Pac-12 honorable mention honors in 2014.
tourBios.personal: Fan of Seattle Seahawks and Seattle Mariners...Favorite athletes are Russell Wilson, Felix Hernandez, Earl Thomas and Robinson Cano...Dream foursome would include Fred Couples, Ken Griffey, Jr., and Arnold Palmer...Favorite course is Quintero GC and favorite professional teams are the Seattle Seahawks and Seattle Mariners.

dyn.dynBios: 2011 Player of the Year, Freshman of the Year, Conference Champion
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T26th in 2014 at the PC Financial Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 94th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
